lead_paragraph: C.J. Cron's second homer of the night soared over the left field fence and ended a remarkable power display in a ballpark that doesn't set off these types of fireworks very often.

headline.print_headline: Cron's 2nd Homer Ends Angels' Wild 11-9 Victory Over Tigers
